data.description: Step into this stunning home bursting with character, nestled in the heart of Denison. It's been loved by one family for 37 years and now awaits its next chapter. The main floor offers two cozy living spaces, a spacious addition perfect as a main bedroom or family hangout, a large kitchen ideal for gatherings, a bathroom, and convenient laundry. Upstairs, discover three roomy bedrooms with charming custom bookshelves and an updated bathroom. Outside, enjoy three spacious garages accessible from the alley or 16th Street, a patio, and a big yard ready for gardening adventures. With beautiful hardwood floors throughout almost 2,000 square feet of living space and all appliances included, this home is ready for new memories. Give us a call to schedule a tour today!
